a missing person?

01:48.358 --> 01:49.776
- He's been gone all night.

01:49.776 --> 01:51.737
Name's Conrad Roy III.

01:51.737 --> 01:54.031
It's unusual him
being gone all night?

01:54.031 --> 01:57.409
- Absolutely. His phone's off,
straight to voice mail.

01:57.409 --> 01:58.952
