<i>how old is he, 18?</i>

02:01.621 --> 02:03.040
<i>I don't want to hear</i>

02:03.040 --> 02:04.833
<i>any of that "24 hour,</i>
<i>he's an adult" crap.</i>

02:04.833 --> 02:06.168
<i>He always comes home.</i>

02:06.168 --> 02:08.462
<i>This is where he sleeps.</i>

02:08.462 --> 02:11.298
