<i>he'd up and disappear?</i>

02:33.153 --> 02:36.073
- Drugs? He into drugs?

02:36.073 --> 02:38.116
- I mean, a little pot.

02:38.116 --> 02:39.785

<i>You there, David?</i>

02:39.785 --> 02:41.411

<i>Go ahead, dispatch.</i>

02:41.411 --> 02:43.622
We've got a possible
<i>sighting of a black F-250</i>

02:43.622 --> 02:45.707
<i>at the Kmart parking lot,</i>
<i>nine miles away.</i>

02:45.707 --> 02:47.000
- Copy.

03:47.018 --> 03:50.689
