04:27.517 --> 04:28.935
- Hey, hey, hey. Hold up.
- Back up.

04:28.935 --> 04:30.520
- Hold up. Who are you?
What's your name?

04:30.520 --> 04:31.897
- You want to know
my fucking name?

04:31.897 --> 04:33.523
Check in the fucking glove box.

04:33.523 --> 04:35.567
That's my grandson's truck!

04:35.567 --> 04:37.736
Let me by! Let me by!

04:37.736 --> 04:39.738
This is my grandson's truck.
