16:06.966 --> 16:08.634
No.

16:15.683 --> 16:17.685
- Why are there bags
in the hallway?

16:17.685 --> 16:20.104
- Uh, New Hampshire.
We're leaving in the morning.

16:20.104 --> 16:21.606
Remember?
- What?

16:21.606 --> 16:23.274
We're going
to the lake house.

16:23.274 --> 16:26.027
- It's been on the calendar
since the same time last year

16:26.027 --> 16:28.529
and the year before that
and the...

16:29.947 --> 16:32.325
- I can't go.
It's Conrad's funeral.

16:32.325 --> 16:34.744
