your dad can get away.

16:42.460 --> 16:44.795
- Yeah.
- I don't care. I'm not going.

16:52.220 --> 16:54.889
I have to be there.

16:54.889 --> 16:58.184
I have to see his mom.

16:58.184 --> 17:01.896
