18:22.977 --> 18:24.770
Riley.

18:27.607 --> 18:30.192
I'm so sorry, Mrs. Roy.

18:31.569 --> 18:33.779
I'm always here.
I know.

18:33.779 --> 18:36.407
- I'm so sorry.
- Thank you.

18:49.587 --> 18:52.798
- Mrs. Roy, I'm Gail Carter.

18:52.798 --> 18:55.718
Uh, I'm sorry--
so sorry for your loss.

18:55.718 --> 18:57.053
- Thank you.

18:57.053 --> 18:58.971
I can't imagine
what you're going through.

18:58.971 --> 19:00.973
I don't know what I would do--
- Michelle?

19:22.453 --> 19:25.247
That kid was born
with the ocean in his blood.

19:26.624 --> 19:29.502
