20:02.702 --> 20:05.079
- I remember that trip.

20:05.079 --> 20:07.707
He came back happy.

20:11.085 --> 20:14.672
Strange that someone
so close to him

20:14.672 --> 20:16.590
and we never met.

20:16.590 --> 20:17.883
- Oh.

20:17.883 --> 20:19.802
