it was appropriate.

21:45.763 --> 21:47.890
- No, no. Yeah, of course.

21:47.890 --> 21:49.600
Excuse me. Sorry.

21:49.600 --> 21:52.520
Mrs. Roy, I'm gonna take off.

21:52.520 --> 21:53.896
- Okay. Thanks, Rob.

21:57.191 --> 21:59.235
