Of course.

21:59.235 --> 22:00.986
- Rob?

22:00.986 --> 22:03.656
- Yeah.
- This is Michelle Carter.

22:07.576 --> 22:11.664
- I really appreciate
your friendship with Conrad.

22:11.664 --> 22:15.167
